title: FK Lokomotiva Gradsko
text: FK Lokomotiva Gradsko () is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club from <a href="Gradsko%20Municipality">Gradsko</a>, <a href="North%20Macedonia">North Macedonia</a>. They are currently competing in the <a href="Macedonian%20Second%20Football%20League">Macedonian Second League</a> (East Division).
